Getting the Code¶

You can get the latest genapp source code here:

https://github.com/cloudbees/genapp

If you can’t see the genapp repository (e.g. you get a 404 error), verify that you’re signed into github as the repository is currently private. If you still can’t see the repository, contact CloudBees for access.
